-- FHB Bank Falls to Month-Low on Hungarian Financial Tax Report
-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 2012-04-11T08:26:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-11/fhb-bank-falls-to-month-low-on-hungarian-financial-tax-report.html
Foldhitel es Jelzalogbank Nyrt. ,
the Hungarian mortgage lender known as FHB, fell to the lowest
in more than a month after news website Origo said Hungary plans
to introduce a financial transaction tax next year.  The shares dropped 2.5 percent to 538 forint by 10:09 a.m.
in Budapest, the weakest intraday level since March 7.  To contact the reporter on this story:
